            div(class="filter-info")
              div(class="row")
                div(class="col-6")
                  div(class="form-group")
                    label(for="exampleFormControlSelect1") Type of Product:
                    select(class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1" name="type_cloth" data-select)
                      option
                      option Watch
                      option Jewellery
                      option Clothes
                      option Shoes
                      option Bags
                div(class="col-6")
                  div(class="form-group d-none select-clothes" data-show-clothes data-show)
                    label(for="exampleFormControlSelect2") Down or Upper Body?
